msgstr ""
"It seems your track record has caught up to you. The guard's crew have heard"
" enough of the crimes you've been committing, and while they have their "
"hands full at the moment, they can't risk letting you into the sector "
"without a fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1069
