#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1192
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"This sector would have once been a safe haven for you and your crew, but "
"ever since the Rebel attack and the sequential Coalition invasion, this "
"sector has become a no man's land. If that wasn't bad enough, pirates have "
"also been drawn into this place hoping to score easy scrap. Watch your step "
"and always be on guard."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1200
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1202
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"In a shocking turn of events, a group of pirates has somehow taken over the "
"entry beacon. Whatever Federation resistance there was here has almost "
"certainly been destroyed, leaving the outlaws to be able to let anyone they "
"want to enter. Of course, the Rebels and the Coalition aren't exactly happy "
"with this outcome, and so have been trying their hardest to break through "
"the pirate's fleet."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1204
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1206
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate guard soon hails you. On the video screen, a tall, strong woman "
"with scars all over her arms greets you. \"Ah, what do we have here, fellas?"
" A Renegade? My, my, that's quite rare around these parts. Still flying that"
" Federation banner, I see? Well, don't keep me from your important little "
"journey. We aren't letting everyone through though. As I'm sure you are well"
" aware, this sector is a bit of a hellzone. Although, if you give us some "
"scrap, that might pull our attention away from this post for a bit.\" She "
"chuckles menacingly and winks."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1208
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Prepare for combat!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1210
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You lock your weapons onto the guard and move in to attack."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1213
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1219
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Pay the fee."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1221
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Good choice, kid.\" The pirate nods before shutting off the call, the ship"
" quickly moving to assist on the defense now that you are no longer in their"
" way."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1228
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/text"
msgstr "(Purple Beard) \"Let us pass....Sarah...\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1230
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"She stares at Purple Beard for a few seconds before chuckling and shaking "
"her head. \"Whatever you say, boss. Here, for the road ahead.\" She winks "
"and transfers over a weapon and some supplies."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1236
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "(Nights) Nights demands free passage!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1238
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"That'ssss where you're misssstaken, bucko. I am Captain Nightssss, and I will be passssing through your checkpoint without paying a ssssingle fragment of ssssscrap. The only quesssstion issss, will I be adding the hull of your sssship to my own richessss? Well? Do we underssstand each other?\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe guard growls, the ship's weapons powering on \"You think I care about a slime like *you*?! You know what, forget the bribe, I want your *head*!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1246
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_kaz\"]/text"
msgstr "(Kazaaakplethkilik) Tell them they are in the presence of a legend."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1248
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_kaz\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You are being in the presence of the great Kazaaakplethkilik Tiiikazpakaziiika! If you are not standing down, then your head will hit the floor before you are realizing I am cutting it off!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe guard gasps. \"It... it's an honor. Of course, you may go as you please.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"I am needing some extra scrap for your time. You are giving?\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe guard sighs and meekly nods before giving the legendary pirate what he wants."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1259
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_tuco\"]/text"
msgstr "(Tuco) Intimidate the guard."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1261
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_tuco\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Hah! You think a greenhorn like you can shake down the likes of me, the Dread Pirate Tuco?\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"The Dread Pirate Tuco??\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"You listen here. Not only may I go freely where I wish, I demand compensation for such an insult!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Y-yes, of course, Tuco.\" The pirate guard dispenses some scrap your way.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Be seein' you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1274
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_A55\"]/text"
msgstr "(A55) Transmit access code."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1276
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_A55\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Arr, see this code? Do ye know who I am?\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Captain A55? What business do you have here?\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Ain't none o' yers! Bein' that I bring many a successful booty to these lands, best step aside, aye?\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"Of course, A55. You can go as you please.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"An' top us off while yer at it!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1289
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"human_angel\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Angel Crew) \"This ship is empowered by the Syndicate to go where it "
"pleases.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1291
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_START_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"human_angel\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The guard is profusely apologetic. \"Of course, please allow us to present "
"you with a tribute. That's a very nice ship that you've taken there.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1309
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears the guard ship is sending out a distress signal to a nearby ASB "
"platform! Brace for impact!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1311
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/text"
