msgstr "An unvisited location."

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:1382
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_REINFORCEMENTS_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You receive a hail from a elite pirate ship. \"Hope you understand this is nothin' personal, but you killed our guard and that's something we just can't allow!\"\n"
"\n"
"\tHowever, before the fight can truly start, you detect that the Coalition and MFK fleets in the distance have also turned their guns on the pirate ship. It's an all-out brawl now!"

